---
title: Baja-Style Blackened Beef Strips with Garlic Rice & Smokey Slaw
description: There’s a hint of smokiness in the air and it’s coming from these beef! The All-American spice works magic when cooked onto
this fresh seafood and served on top of a bed of rice. Not to mention, the smokey aioli tossed through the slaw. It’s a firestorm of flavour tonight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/669464eaba3419004e45a54c-d5aab8ca.jpeg
